[
    {
        "Key": "hi01.1",
        "Speaker": "O卡罗琳",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "看你忙挺久了，别太压榨自己，在营地多休息一会也没关系的。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "choice.01",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "谢谢，你也辛苦了",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "choice.02",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这里问题还没解决",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page01.1",
        "Speaker": "O卡罗琳",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "要是真关心我，就别随随便便在零区内失联。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page02.1",
        "Speaker": "O卡罗琳",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你老是这样说，但事情哪有能做完的时候。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "hi02.1",
        "Speaker": "O卡罗琳",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这次任务太紧急，我都没来得及带上电热水壶，好累……",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "choice.03",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "我带了，待会给你",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "choice.04",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "保温杯代替一下？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page03.1",
        "Speaker": "O卡罗琳",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "嗯嗯？！你怎么会随身带这个！",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page04.1",
        "Speaker": "O卡罗琳",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "不可能的，我不接受。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "hi03.1",
        "Speaker": "O卡罗琳",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这次出了这么大的事，公司内估计乱成一团了吧。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "choice.05",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "陶总能解决的",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "choice.06",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "这边也得加快了",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page05.1",
        "Speaker": "O卡罗琳",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "也是，老板应该早有准备。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page06.1",
        "Speaker": "O卡罗琳",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "知道了，工作狂。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "hi04.1",
        "Speaker": "O卡罗琳",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "欢迎回来，是要先吃饭，先洗澡，还是先交接任务？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "choice.07",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "事已至此先吃饭吧",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "choice.08",
        "Speaker": "",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "没有隐藏选项吗？",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page07.1",
        "Speaker": "O卡罗琳",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "今天的午餐是——锵锵，任选18种口味的压缩饼干。",
        "disable": 0
    },
    {
        "Key": "page08.1",
        "Speaker": "O卡罗琳",
        "WwiseEventID": "",
        "zh_CN": "你要是想再义务加班几个小时，我也没意见。",
